    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# service-subscription model tracks service-level subscription agreements\n\n`powerhouse/service-subscription` (12 ops) manages subscription agreements at the service level. Distinct from [[subscription-instance model tracks active customer subscriptions with lifecycle state]] which tracks individual customer instances.\n\n## Cross-Model References\n\n- ServiceOffering \u2192 ServiceSubscription (offering defines what can be subscribed to)\n- May bridge between [[service-offering model defines tiered pricing with option groups and service groups]] and [[subscription-instance model tracks active customer subscriptions with lifecycle state]]\n\n## Position in Ecosystem\n\nService & Pricing zone. Sits between the offering definition and the individual subscription instance \u2014 the agreement layer.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[ecosystem map]]\n- [[object relations]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:44.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:44.000Z"
    }
  },
